6. TECHNICAL ARCHITECTURE WHITEPAPER

(Full whitepaper content integrated – key sections)

The whitepaper elaborates on the system‑of‑systems approach, the bidirectional Digital Twin, and detailed component architecture. It covers:

· Cognitive Core: AI cluster, quantum backend, neuromorphic nodes, storage fabric.
· Edge Architecture: Micro data centers with K3s, autonomy mode, local data buffering.
· Connectivity Fabric: 400G backbone, private 5G, QKD.
· Data Fabric: Kafka, schema registry, stream processing, Iceberg data lake.
· Zero Trust Security: Micro‑segmentation, identity‑centric, continuous verification.

